		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move the cursor -
                  <font color="#00FF00">D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open the mini map (during battles) -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open the Battle Menu (during battles).End the conversation, the event -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Start Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select action. Check the movement of the char (during battles). Open the Battle Menu (during battles) -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel -
                  <font color="#00FF00">X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Check the status of the character. Mark some locations by a small flag (during battles). The limit is 3 -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump the cursor to other chars (during battles). Move to the next board while checking the status of the chars -
                  <font color="#00FF00">L1 or R1 Buttons</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fast Forward! Hold this button in the conversation, or while seeking a wpn or itm in your storage -
                  <font color="#00FF00">R2 Button</font><br><br>
&nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
